Package: ssdsaver
Version: 0.3.4
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: python3 (>= 3.8), python3-gi, gir1.2-gtk-4.0, gir1.2-adw-1
Maintainer: Andy Savage <andy@example.com>
Description: GUI configurator for log2ram (bundled)
 A modern GTK4/Libadwaita desktop application for configuring and managing
 log2ram on Debian-based systems. Provides an easy-to-use interface for
 adjusting RAM size, sync methods, and service control without using the
 command line.
 .
 This package includes log2ram bundled, so no separate installation is needed.
